[color=orange][b][center]Okay started a new project seen as other source was release and really messed up. Im not going to say im going to release this or anything, its will be run, hopefully 24/7 when its finished and maybe become quite good I hope.
[IMG]http://i258.photobucket.com/albums/hh252/rrrobbbieee/questtab.jpg[/img]
Dont come here to flame, its just progress and its proberly not so advanced right now. If anyone has anything that can help my project please do.
Thanks.
Possible Future Forums created by Da 0wnz - http://pwnscapev3.webs.com/index.htm Youtube - www.youtube.com/user/pwnscapechannel Current Forum Url - www.pwnscape.co.nr XAT CHAT WOOHOO. www.pwnscapechat.co.nr
[IMG]http://i258.photobucket.com/albums/hh252/rrrobbbieee/login-1.jpg[/img]
Needed List: [i]All 477 Interfaces that are compatible with 377 client. Someone who is good with graphics for client backgrounds, banners for forums, etc. Msql highscores ? Possible, who knows :P Okay with the health when a player dies sometimes 0hp is not displayed as a full red hp bar. so it looks like they die on full hp? If someone can help with this will rep greatly lol. Bluurs headicons, Nooby question but does can anyone help me with adding the prayer headicons ^^
[/i] Targets. [i]Amazing 100% Rs2 Pve, Including ~~ -100% Kq just like rs, no faults. -100% Jad - Just tweaked delta's a little, modify healers? Tell me what you think. > -100% Dagganoths - Nearly there, anyone got old footage of dags? might help. -100% GIANT MOLE - CAWZ WE LEIKS TEH MOLEY -100% KBD And if anyone has any idea's of old PVE npc's I could try, please post. Dont say anything beyond 477 deob
Quest - Full RFD. With correctly quest interface all mini parts and bosses at end, :D [/i]
